description: The USB2HABM6RA 6-foot USB A to Mini USB Cable features one USB A Male connector and one right-angled Mini USB B connector, providing a simple way for connecting your digital camera (Canon, Sony, Hewlett Packard) to a host computer. This USB A to right angle Mini B cable also delivers a cost-effective way to maximize the file transfer performance of your MP3 player, PDA, or digital camcorder. The right-angled Mini USB connector allows the computer and the connected USB peripheral to be positioned nearly flush against a wall or other surface, by eliminating the space that would typically be required to accommodate a ''straight'' connection from the cable into the USB port or peripheral device.
title: StarTech.com Mini USB Cable - A to Right Angle Mini B - 6 Feet (USB2HABM6RA)
